OL,3,CCrematorium should relocate away from
OL,4,COverdale hospital, Health Minister says
OL,6,FJersey's Crematorium Services will
OL,7,Ftemporarily relocate whilst work takes
OL,8,Fplace at the Overdale Hospital Site.
OL,10,FThe crematorium has been based next to
OL,11,Fthe Overdale site for 35 years, and
OL,12,Fthe current plan is for services to
OL,13,Freturn here once the new hospital is
OL,14,Fbuilt.
OL,16,FIn the meantime, islanders mourning
OL,17,Floved ones will gather at The Royal
OL,18,FShowground in Trinity.
