OL,3,CCrematorium should relocate away from
OL,4,COverdale hospital, Health Minister says
OL,6,FThe interim move ensures services can
OL,7,Fcontinue without disruption from
OL,8,Fconstruction work.
OL,10,FDeputy Tom Binet, Jersey's Health
OL,11,FMinister, explains: "This is another
OL,12,Fstep along the way on the whole
OL,13,Fprocess. The last thing you want is
OL,14,Fconstruction site noise, so this will
OL,15,Ftake that out of the equation.
OL,17,F"There's work happening on site - the
OL,18,Frefurbishment of the Jersey ward
OL,19,Fbuildings to become the site
OL,20,Fheadquarters."
