OL,3,CCrematorium should relocate away from
OL,4,COverdale hospital, Health Minister says
OL,6,FHowever, Deputy Binet has also told
OL,7,FITV News that the crematorium should
OL,8,Fnever return to its former site, and a
OL,9,Fnew permanent replacement should be
OL,10,Ffound.
OL,12,FHe explains: "On a personal level, I'd
OL,13,Frather not see the Crematorium get
OL,14,Fused again as a crematory for services.
OL,16,F"I'm hoping that while the building is
OL,17,Fgoing on, we can find another site for
OL,18,Fa crematorium, build a new one, and
OL,19,Fthen when it leaves here, we can go
OL,20,Fstraight to the new facility. That's
OL,21,Fmy hope.
