OL,3,CCrematorium should relocate away from
OL,4,COverdale hospital, Health Minister says
OL,6,F"(The old crematorium) needs a lot of
OL,7,Fmoney spent on it, so rather than
OL,8,Fspending money on an old facility,
OL,9,Fspend the money on a new one.
OL,11,F"I think a lot of people wouldn't feel
OL,12,Fcomfortable about having a crematorium
OL,13,Flocated right next to a hospital."
OL,15,FConnetable Andy Jehan, Jersey's
OL,16,FInfrastructure Minister, hopes the
OL,17,Ftemporary site will provide a "quiet
OL,18,Fand respectful" place while Overdale
OL,19,Fwork continues.
