OL,3,CCrematorium should relocate away from
OL,4,COverdale hospital, Health Minister says
OL,6,FHe explains: "This location has been
OL,7,Fdesigned to be somewhere where people
OL,8,Fcan have a service in peace and quiet,
OL,9,Fwhich is also respectful.
OL,11,F"We've worked very closely with
OL,12,Freligious groups and also undertakers
OL,13,Fto make sure that we can deliver
OL,14,Fsomething that is better than we had
OL,15,Fbefore.
OL,17,F"When I first walked in here, I was
OL,18,Freally impressed with the calmness of
OL,19,Fthe building. It's been transformed,
OL,20,Fand the team should be congratulated
OL,21,Fon that work.
